snippet.title: A Whole New Perspective - BeyondSMBWii Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
this thing is a solo project ive been working on during freetime and ive got enough to showcase it intime for the direct. its a fan project/mod for new super mario bros wii that im really passionate about!

edit: forgot to mention the direct was the "NHD Holiday Direct" by tmolter/toms
